:"entry","text":"transgenic [ˌtrænzˈdʒenɪk]","headword":"transgenic"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.转基因的，基因改造的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎transgenic plant转基因植物"},{"type":"entry","text":"cell division 细胞分裂","headword":"cell division"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"}]},{"number":1910,"blocks":[{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：Heredity is all about the transfer of characteristics from parent to"},{"type":"text","text":"offspring. （遗传是指从父母转移特点给后代。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Heredity is amazing. （遗传真的很令人吃惊。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"},{"type":"example","text":"A：The development of genetic technology makes it possible for"},{"type":"text","text":"human beings to control genetic diseases by intervening in the reproductive"},{"type":"text","text":"process. （基因技术的发展使人类通过干预生殖过程来控制遗传疾病变"},{"type":"text","text":"得可能。）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Modern technology is so great. （现代技术真是太伟大了。）"}]}]}